{"tid":1187720,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"秀茂坪男子墮樓亡","createTime":"2019-06-06T00:09:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-06T01:49:14.000Z","uid":3090,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8544f4d906b13910ac93fd8f45fb3eb0a0a30465","tid":1187720,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T00:09:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fLvLeMe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfLvLeMe.png&h=ec367a8e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BK1KvjA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBK1KvjA.png&h=7f7879c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n男子從秀賢樓墮下。黎地偉攝<br />\n<br />\n秀茂坪邨秀賢樓，早上6時許，一名男子從大廈高處墮下，倒地昏迷不醒，街坊發現報警，救護員到場，證實男子已當場死亡，警員封鎖現場展開調查，死者姓王56歲，相信從住所墮下，案件初步並無可疑。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」：<a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=HGsIALD6rBmJFWdd%2FklElo6aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=10de4796\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.openup.hk</a>"},{"pid":"59396589a8242e98e717960577e14257ea7eca78","tid":1187720,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T00:10:19.000Z","msg":"有腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16b625deec72d2bbad429051a0e28df67242f217","tid":1187720,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59396589a8242e98e717960577e14257ea7eca78","tid":1187720,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T00:10:19.000Z","msg":"有腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T00:21:32.000Z","msg":"晨早流流就跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e806fda9901f0f1ea1fe4e1